products.description: The VR rebellion continues with the ASUS Dual-fan RX 580 8GB OC Edition. Auto-Extreme manufacturing technology with Super Alloy Power II components ensures premium quality and reliability while dual fans provide quieter and cooler gaming environment. GPU Tweak II with XSplit Gamecaster delivers ultimate monitoring and streaming control.
